{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"20a87a83d9","title":"在谈判中采取灵活战术，实行强硬路线","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5a6e7e121a","index":0,"year":1951,"month":11,"day":19,"articleId":"20a87a83d9"}],"tags":[{"id":"625c516d2c","name":"朝鲜战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d20738c862","name":"世界形势","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a1a519b753","type":"paragraph","text":"在谈判中来取灵活战术，实行强硬路线","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"751be9f249","type":"paragraph","text":"致毛泽东电","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"cb776648a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1951年11月19日）北京致克拉索夫斯基：","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"00a99be5e7","type":"paragraph","text":"转毛泽东同志","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"d7c0ac4ea8","type":"paragraph","text":"“毛泽东同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"e723e803ae","type":"paragraph","text":"您关于朝鲜停战谈判问题的电报收到了。我们同意您对谈判目前形势的评价。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"824d5f9e67","type":"paragraph","text":"近来谈判全过程表明，美国人虽然在拖延谈判，但是他们更需要尽快结束谈判。","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"52e8c96545","type":"paragraph","text":"这是根据总的国际形势得出的结论。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"20df6083c8","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为正确的做法是，中朝方面应继续在谈判中采取灵活战术，实行强硬路线，不能有急躁和尽快结束谈判的表现。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"b917281e9b","type":"paragraph","text":"在确定分界线和在1-2个边防站进行检查问题上，我们认为你们的立场是止确的","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"6fb695fe75","type":"paragraph","text":"我们还同意关于履行检查职能的委员会人选问题","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"79d0fc7696","type":"paragraph","text":"在交换战仔问题上，您的立场完全正确，敌人很难对此提出异议。","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"deec2de35f","type":"paragraph","text":"至于在签订停战协定后，为进一步解决朝鲜问题而召开会议的可能的方案，我们认为，召开目前谈判双方政治代表的政治会议是适宜的，但必须要有北、南朝鲜的代表参加。","index":12,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"716dab8e71","type":"paragraph","text":"菲利波夫","index":13,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"c71d9b20a1","type":"paragraph","text":"1951年11月19日”《朝鲜战争：俄国档案馆的解密文件》","index":14,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"128c3386bd","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》（下册）第1108页","index":15,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"},{"id":"b931b00b76","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷九第209页","index":16,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9"}],"page":{"id":"fb6f6070b6","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"20a87a83d9","start":2754,"end":2754}}}},"__N_SSG":true}